comments: Paul (PHX) and Barnes (SAC) briefly engage and separate off ball.
Ayton (PHX) jumps vertically contesting the shot attempt by Barnes (SAC) at the basket.
Holmes (SAC) makes marginal contact with Paul (PHX) during the rebound and does not affect his ability to get to the loose ball.
Paul (PHX) makes contact to Holmes's (SAC) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Paul (PHX) sets the screen in Fox's (SAC) path and gives him room to avoid the contact.
Fox (SAC) makes marginal contact with Paul (PHX) during the shot attempt.
Crowder (PHX) makes incidental "high-five" contact with Fox (SAC) after the release that does not affect his jump shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) initiates contact with Paul (PHX) that affects his SQBR.
Holmes (SAC) wraps his arm around Bridges (PHX) while setting the screen and affects his ability to disengage and defend.
Bridges (PHX) maintains a legal guarding position on Hield (SAC) during the driving shot attempt.
Crowder (PHX) makes contact with Holmes's (SAC) arm and affects his shot attempt.
Fox (SAC) maintains a legal guarding position while contesting Booker's (PHX) shot attempt.
Ayton (PHX) makes marginal contact with Fox (SAC) at the end of the drive.
Bridges (PHX) makes marginal contact with Fox's (SAC) arm after he releases the shot attempt.
Correctly called delay of game violation.
Booker (PHX) makes marginal contact with Bjelica (SAC) while attempting to move around the screen.
Booker (PHX) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
Paul (PHX) commits a take foul on Hield (SAC).
